These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, september, april, february
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku, writing
House: tower, wooden, futuristic, palace
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the tower house##1
 3. the futuristic house is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 4. the tower house is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
 6. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the futuristic house is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is not the palace house##6
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
10. the wooden house is the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the futuristic house##8
12. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
13. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the right of the palace house##8
14. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the futuristic house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Birthday    | december         | february     | april     | september         |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | writing    | sudoku     | magic-tricks |
| House   | tower       | wooden | palace | futuristic       |

