.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, airplane, bus
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, librarian, pilot
City: marseilles, berlin, london, hamburg
 1. the librarian is not to the right of the pilot##8
 2. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
 3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person driving the bus is the freelancer##1
 5. the electrician is not the person driving the airplane##6
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Transport   | airplane          | car      | bus      | quad-bike   |
| Job        | librarian     | electrician | freelancer | pilot      |
| City      | hamburg | berlin    | marseilles  | london |

