.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, reading, sudoku
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, french, mexican
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, alhambra, tiparillo, cain
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 2. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the cain-smoker##5
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is not the american##6
 6. the american is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 7. the american is not to the right of the mexican##8
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the french##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading  | filmmaking | sudoku | card-games |
| Nationality   | argentine  | american      | mexican | french        |
| Cigar     | ritmeester | tiparillo       | cain    | alhambra     |

