.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, horror, mystery, thriller
4 different games are played: canasta, go, scrabble, billiard
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, baking, photography, drawing
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 2. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the left of the person playing go##8
 3. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##8
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
 7. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's hobby is photography##1
11. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | thriller | horror    | mystery |
| Game   | scrabble    | go     | canasta   | billiard     |
| Hobby   | board-games | photography   | baking | drawing    |

