 3. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the fan of classical##6
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is the fan of classical##1
 9. the person traveling to miami is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
10. the fan of soul is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the fan of soul is not to the left of the person traveling to miami##8

.:: Answer ::.
