.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, grapes, plum, potato
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, cola, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: rat, snake, pony, goat
 1. the person eating plum is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is not the owner of the snake##6
 3. the owner of the pony is somewhere between the person eating grapes and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 4. the owner of the snake is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
 5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the owner of the pony is the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 8. the owner of the goat is between the person eating blueberry and the owner of the pony##2
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person eating blueberry##8
10. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person eating potato##8
11. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | grapes      | plum      | potato | blueberry |
| Beverage   | cola | fanta    | soy-milk | sprite     |
| Pet   | rat    | pony | goat  | snake |

