 4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 6. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 7. the person who's sport is handball is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
 8. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##8
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person who's sport is handball##8
10. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
11. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
12. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
13. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
