 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the right of the person eating plum##8
 2. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person eating artichoke and the person playing scrabble##7
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person eating pumpkin##8
 4. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person eating plum##8
10. the person eating cherry is not to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
11. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
13. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
14. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | drawing    | magic-tricks | woodworking | fishing    |
| Game   | scrabble  | monopoly    | mah-jongg      | go |
